text: Dasht is a town and tehsil (a unit of government) of Kech District in the Balochistan province of Pakistan. The town is at 28°36'30N 66°18'50E with an altitude of 1796 metres (5895 feet). In 1998, 58,621 people lived in Dasht. Category:Tehsils of Balochistan Category:Mastung District
title: Dasht (Kharan)
